{
  "name": "RPlog_The_Interrogation_of_Han_Solo",
  "title": "The Interrogation of Han Solo",
  "summary": "Held in the Port Security Office detention cell on the Corporate Sector world of Etti IV, the captured New Republic general Han Solo is dragged from his cell by a hulking scar-faced CSA interrogator while the cold Authority enforcer Piper looks on. Solo deflects the brute's furious questioning about his rank and mission with flat, sardonic non-answers, refusing to confirm anything. The session escalates when the unhinged torturer Singe arrives with a briefcase of instruments, intent on \"preparing\" Solo for questioning with a cellular calibrator and drugs. As Singe shocks Solo and then his own bumbling subordinate Scar, a chaotic brawl erupts; Solo headbutts and kicks free, and in the struggle Singe is fatally impaled on his own torture device. The grief-maddened Scar hurls Solo across the room before knocking himself unconscious against a wall. A thoroughly disgusted Piper finally draws her blaster, orders the battered Solo returned to his cell, and storms out after demanding the mess be cleaned and the prisoner guarded on pain of death.",
